{"tid":119322,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"搭載虹膜識別技術？iPhone 8 十周年版傳售價近$8000","createTime":"2017-02-13T15:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T16:54:03.000Z","uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6155b04c5d06dcd06614c9c17603318f7f2c0a","tid":119322,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20170213_iphone8_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20170213_iphone8_01.jpg&h=be7fde60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔少網友上年忍手唔換 iPhone 7，相信都係打算等埋 2017 年部十周年版 iPhone 再作決定吧？不過早前就有消息傳出，指十周年版 iPhone 或索價 1,000 美元，成為史上最貴的 iPhone。<br />\n<br />\n賣得貴有玄機？<br />\n <br />\n1,000 美金、換算約港幣 7,756 左右，到底呢部 iPhone 點解賣咁貴呢？<br />\n<br />\n除了「十周年」值得紀念之外，更有傳在除了曲面 OLED 之外，十周年版 iPhone 8 更會搭載虹膜識別技術，可透過辨識虹膜認證用戶身份並解鎖手機，另外亦會加入無線充電功能並改用雙玻璃面設計。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.ringhk.com/editor/news2016/20161117_iphone8_oled_01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ringhk.com%2Feditor%2Fnews2016%2F20161117_iphone8_oled_01.jpg&h=63fa28e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過之前就有傳因供應問題，蘋果在 2017 年並不會為所有 iPhone 改配 OLED 螢幕，當中 5 吋版本的「細機」會延續過去的設計定位，而只有十周年版的 iPhone 8，先會起用類似 Galaxy S7 edge 的曲面 OLED 螢幕設計，定同現時的亮黑 iPhone 7 Plus 相似。<br />\n<br />\n而現時亮黑 iPhone 7 Plus 亮分別定價 $7,388 (128GB) 及 $8,288 (256GB)，如果十周年版 iPhone 容量由 128GB 起跳的話，1,000 美金呢個價錢似乎仍屬合理。"},{"pid":"f394c7bf925aab2833062c284ace13c94539bb0e","tid":119322,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"傳傳傳傳傳傳傳傳傳傳傳傳傳傳<br />\n<br />\n最後出舊屎咪又係狗衝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21ff547b017109d622dfb9b6b9d94cc8d8c03b4","tid":119322,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:07:38.000Z","msg":"好快又一車車羊牯排住隊送錢俾apple"},{"pid":"21068d4803871efdfa05457af6df040a31e1132e","tid":119322,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:14:20.000Z","msg":"Apple出咩新機大把人鳩衝，得一個字，炒<br />\n先下手為強"},{"pid":"9fe0b53a3de269e16feebce585dcc2af5d74722e","tid":119322,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T16:54:03.000Z","msg":"炒撚爆佢，炒足幾個月好過你返工"}]}